# Safe Order — Task Tracker

## Step 1: Project Scaffolding ✅
## Step 2: Authentication & User Management ✅
## Step 3: Order Pipeline & Core Business Logic ✅

- [x] Orders router (`routers/orders.py`) — 11 endpoints:
  - POST / — create order (merchant)
  - GET /link/{token} — access order via unique link
  - POST /link/{token}/fill — customer fills delivery info
  - GET /pipeline/counts — pipeline stage counts
  - GET /pipeline/{status} — orders by status
  - GET /all — all merchant orders
  - GET /{id} — order details (with access control)
  - GET /{id}/tracking — tracking events
  - GET /track/{code} — public tracking by code
  - PATCH /{id}/status — advance pipeline stage (with transition validation)
  - GET /customer/by-phone/{phone} — customer order history
- [x] Smart Badge computation: SAFE_PAY > RISK > LOYAL > NEW
- [x] Status transition validation (CONFIRMATION→PREPARATION→DISPATCH→DELIVERY→DELIVERED/RETURN)
- [x] Risk prediction integration (auto-calculates on customer fill)
- [x] Tracking event auto-creation

## Step 4: Safe Pay — Simulated Payment System ✅

- [x] Payments router (`routers/payments.py`) — 4 endpoints:
  - POST /process — simulated CIB/Dahabia/BaridiMob (always succeeds in demo)
  - GET /order/{id} — order payment history
  - GET /wallet/{phone} — customer wallet summary
  - POST /refund/{id} — refund deposit for returned orders

## Step 5: Safe Track ✅

- [x] Tracking router (`routers/tracking.py`) — 3 endpoints:
  - GET /track/{code} — public tracking with timeline
  - POST /track/{code}/remark — customer adds remark (with date detection → D-1 alert)
  - GET /by-phone/{phone} — customer order history

## Step 6: Feedback, Trust Score & Stats ✅

- [x] Feedback router (`routers/feedback.py`) — 5 endpoints:
  - POST /submit — post-delivery feedback (1-5 stars, criteria, comment)
  - GET /order/{id} — order feedback
  - GET /merchant/{id} — merchant feedbacks
  - GET /trust-score/{id} — Trust Score (0-100, levels: bronze/silver/gold/platinum)
  - POST /analyze-return/{id} — trigger AI return analysis
- [x] Trust Score calculation (weighted: delivery 40%, rating 30%, volume 15%, Safe Pay 15%)
- [x] Stats router (`routers/stats.py`) — 2 endpoints:
  - GET /dashboard — full merchant stats (rates, revenue, best sellers, wilayas, feedbacks)
  - GET /insights — Safe Insights (AI cause breakdown + recommendations)
- [x] Admin router (`routers/admin.py`) — 5 endpoints:
  - GET /dashboard — global platform stats
  - GET /users — user list (filterable)
  - PATCH /users/{id}/toggle-active — activate/deactivate
  - GET /orders — all orders (filterable)
  - GET /merchants — merchant list with profiles

